headline: Founder & CEO - Simplista
summary: Clean and complete item data is table stakes for an efficient retail operation, yet retailers and brands struggle to quickly and accurately exchange and transmit the hundreds of pieces of data required to sell a single product. Simplista provides real-time automated item setup, enabling brands to list their products into stores and ecommerce in hours (not weeks or months), and retailers to automatically capture brand changes as they happen. Equally important, our tech finds and fixes gaps and errors in the retailer’s back end, to ensure 100% accurate product information flows into every application that relies on item data. name: Gil Dror
headline: Chief Technology Officer - SmartSense by Digi
summary:
Greetings,
As we approach the National Retail Federation show, I would like to extend an invite to colleagues with a technical inclination or those involved in innovation within the retail space.

I specialize in the application of SmartSense technologies — leveraging IoT, machine learning, and advanced analytics to empower retailers to make informed, data-driven decisions. Our solutions are crafted to ensure operational efficiency, reduce waste, and enhance both the in-store and backend aspects of retail management.

I am interested in meeting individuals who are:

- Technical Experts: If you have a background in developing or implementing technical solutions for retail, and are interested in exchanging insights or discussing advancements in IoT and analytics, a conversation with you would be beneficial.

- Innovation Leaders: For those responsible for driving innovation in retail, particularly if you are looking to improve operational efficiency and customer experience through data insights, I believe a discussion around SmartSense's capabilities could be of value.

If your objectives align with creating a more efficient, data-enhanced retail environment, I welcome the opportunity to connect during NRF to see how we can work together towards common goals.

Feel free to reach out to me through the NRF portal or directly contact me to arrange a meeting.
